longBusinessSummary: The fund allocates assets among affiliated equity funds and non-affiliated equity funds that participate in Fidelity's FundsNetwork®, and non-affiliated ETFs and sub-advisers. It allocates assets among sub-advisers and underlying funds using proprietary fundamental and quantitative research, considering factors including, but not limited to, performance in different market environments, manager experience and investment style, management company infrastructure, costs, asset size, and portfolio turnover.
